    "custom_liquid_reassurance": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Reassurance",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<!-- Reassurance Section - Mobile Optimized -->\n<section style=\"background: #F5F1E8; padding: 60px 0; width: 100%; margin: 0;\">\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; text-align: center;\">\n<h2 style=\"font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 38px); color: #2d5016; margin-bottom: 25px; line-height: 1.3;\">If You're Unsure, You're Exactly Where You Should Be</h2>\n<p style=\"font-size: clamp(17px, 4vw, 20px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; margin-bottom: 30px;\">Almost everyone who joins the garden starts with the same thoughts:</p>\n<ul style=\"list-style: none; padding: 0; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.9; color: #555; text-align: left; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 30px;\">\n<li style=\"padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1);\">\"I have no rhythm.\"</li>\n<li style=\"padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1);\">\"I don't know anyone.\"</li>\n<li style=\"padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1);\">\"I'm not a dancer.\"</li>\n<li style=\"padding: 10px 0;\">\"What if I feel awkward?\"</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"font-size: clamp(18px, 4.2vw, 20px); line-height: 1.7; color: #2d5016; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 35px;\">That's not a problem.<br>That's the starting point.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
    },
    "custom_liquid_is_this_for_you": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Is This For You",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<!-- This Is Especially For You If Section -->\n<section id=\"is-this-for-you\" style=\"background: white; padding: 60px 0; width: 100%; margin: 0;\">\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #2d5016; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 15px;\">Is This For You?</div>\n<h2 style=\"font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 42px); font-weight: bold; color: #2d5016; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.2;\">This Space Is For You If</h2>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n<ul style=\"list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 30px 0;\">\n<li style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;\">\n<span style=\"position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;\">✓</span>\nYou're a young professional, student, or creative who misses real human connection\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;\">\n<span style=\"position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;\">✓</span>\nYou're comfortable in English, or want a space where language isn't a barrier\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;\">\n<span style=\"position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;\">✓</span>\nYou're curious about dance, but more curious about people\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;\">\n<span style=\"position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;\">✓</span>\nYou want to meet others without small talk, apps, or performance pressure\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); color: #333; margin-bottom: 18px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; line-height: 1.7;\">\n<span style=\"position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2d5016; font-size: 20px;\">✓</span>\nYou believe connection can be learned — and practiced\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"background: #F5F1E8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px 25px; text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px;\">Here, we speak English first. But more importantly, we share a deeper language — touch, presence, and attention.</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: clamp(15px, 3.5vw, 16px); line-height: 1.6; color: #666; font-style: italic;\">It may not be for you if you're looking for a drop-in workout with no community. And that's okay.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
    },
    "custom_liquid_faq": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "FAQ",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<!-- FAQ Section -->\n<section id=\"common-questions\" style=\"background: #F5F1E8; padding: 60px 0; width: 100%; margin: 0;\">\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;\">\n\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #2d5016; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 15px;\">Common Questions</div>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 42px); font-weight: bold; color: #2d5016; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.2;\">Everything You're Wondering</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto;\">No question is too small. Here are the ones we hear most.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n\n    <div class=\"start-here-faq-item\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);\">\n      <button class=\"start-here-faq-btn\" aria-expanded=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4;\">\n        Do I need any dance experience to start?\n        <span class=\"start-here-faq-icon\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"start-here-faq-answer\" style=\"overflow: hidden; max-height: 0; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.3s ease; padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;\">Not at all. Every session is designed for absolute beginners. We start from scratch — how to stand, how to be present, how to listen through touch. No prior dance experience is needed or expected.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"start-here-faq-item\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);\">\n      <button class=\"start-here-faq-btn\" aria-expanded=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4;\">\n        Do I need to bring a partner?\n        <span class=\"start-here-faq-icon\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"start-here-faq-answer\" style=\"overflow: hidden; max-height: 0; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.3s ease; padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;\">No. Most people come alone. We rotate partners during class so everyone gets to dance with different people. In fact, coming solo often makes it easier to connect with the community.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"start-here-faq-item\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);\">\n      <button class=\"start-here-faq-btn\" aria-expanded=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4;\">\n        What should I wear?\n        <span class=\"start-here-faq-icon\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"start-here-faq-answer\" style=\"overflow: hidden; max-height: 0; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.3s ease; padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;\">Comfortable clothes you can move in. For shoes, we recommend either a clean pair of cozy socks, or a second pair of indoor shoes. Avoid thick rubber soles — they grip the floor and make turning difficult. We'll guide you on proper tango shoes once you decide to invest more.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"start-here-faq-item\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);\">\n      <button class=\"start-here-faq-btn\" aria-expanded=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4;\">\n        Is the class taught in English?\n        <span class=\"start-here-faq-icon\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"start-here-faq-answer\" style=\"overflow: hidden; max-height: 0; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.3s ease; padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;\">Yes. All teaching is in English. Under request, we can also offer German, Russian and Greek. The deeper language of tango — presence, touch, listening — transcends words entirely.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"start-here-faq-item\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);\">\n      <button class=\"start-here-faq-btn\" aria-expanded=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4;\">\n        What's the difference between the three options?\n        <span class=\"start-here-faq-icon\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"start-here-faq-answer\" style=\"overflow: hidden; max-height: 0; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.3s ease; padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <div style=\"padding-bottom: 20px;\">\n          <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; margin-bottom: 12px;\"><strong>Enter the Garden</strong> is a one-time introductory event — perfect if you want to get a feel for the space with zero commitment.</p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; margin-bottom: 12px;\"><strong>Regular Classes</strong> are a full course that takes you from zero to dancing. This is the most effective path if you want to actually learn tango.</p>\n          <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333;\"><strong>Weekly Practicas</strong> are open practice sessions — great once you've had some classes and want to apply what you've learned in a relaxed, social setting.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"start-here-faq-item\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);\">\n      <button class=\"start-here-faq-btn\" aria-expanded=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4;\">\n        What if I miss a class?\n        <span class=\"start-here-faq-icon\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"start-here-faq-answer\" style=\"overflow: hidden; max-height: 0; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.3s ease; padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;\">No worries. Students on the multi-week course pass can cover any missed class by attending our Garden Practica during the pass' eligibility cycle, at no extra cost. Life happens — we've built that flexibility in.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"start-here-faq-item\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);\">\n      <button class=\"start-here-faq-btn\" aria-expanded=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4;\">\n        I'm shy. Will I feel awkward?\n        <span class=\"start-here-faq-icon\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"start-here-faq-answer\" style=\"overflow: hidden; max-height: 0; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.3s ease; padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;\">Probably a little — that's normal. Most people feel that way in the first 20 minutes. Then something shifts. Tango is one of the few spaces where being present and quiet is actually an advantage. You don't need to perform or entertain. You just need to show up.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"start-here-faq-item\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.15);\">\n      <button class=\"start-here-faq-btn\" aria-expanded=\"false\" style=\"width: 100%; background: none; border: none; padding: 20px 0; text-align: left; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); font-weight: 600; color: #2d5016; line-height: 1.4;\">\n        Where exactly are you located in Cologne?\n        <span class=\"start-here-faq-icon\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 24px; color: #4E5D22; transition: transform 0.3s ease; line-height: 1;\">+</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"start-here-faq-answer\" style=\"overflow: hidden; max-height: 0; transition: max-height 0.35s ease, padding 0.3s ease; padding-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: clamp(16px, 3.8vw, 18px); line-height: 1.7; color: #333; padding-bottom: 20px;\">\n          Our main studio is located at <strong>Thürmchenswall 21, 50668 Cologne</strong> (Yoga Drop Studio), just a 3-minute walk from <strong>Ebertplatz</strong>.\n          It’s a beautiful, quiet space tucked away from the main street.\n          If you're having trouble finding the entrance, just <a href=\"https://wa.me/491602368723\" style=\"color: #2d5016; font-weight: 600;\">message us on WhatsApp</a>.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- FAQ bottom CTA -->\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; padding: 50px 30px; background: #F9F7F2; border: 1px solid rgba(45,80,22,0.1); border-radius: 20px;\">\n      <h4 style=\"font-size: 22px; color: #4E5D22; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 700;\">Still have a question?</h4>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 30px;\">We love hearing from people before they take the leap.</p>\n      <a href=\"https://wa.me/491602368723?text=Hi!%20I%20have%20a%20question%20before%20joining...\" class=\"safety-btn-primary\" style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; padding: 12px 24px; background: #4E5D22; color: white; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; border-radius: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(45,80,22,0.2); transition: all 0.3s ease; border: 1px solid transparent;\">\n        <span style=\"margin-right: 8px;\">💬</span> Ask us on WhatsApp\n      </a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .start-here-faq-btn[aria-expanded=\"true\"] .start-here-faq-icon {\n    transform: rotate(45deg);\n  }\n\n  .start-here-faq-answer.is-open {\n    max-height: 600px !important;\n    padding-bottom: 0 !important;\n  }\n\n  .safety-btn-primary:hover {\n    background: #3d6b1f !important;\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(45,80,22,0.3) !important;\n  }\n\n  .safety-btn-primary:active {\n    transform: translateY(0);\n  }\n</style>\n\n<script>\n  document.querySelectorAll('.start-here-faq-btn').forEach(function(btn) {\n    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      var isOpen = btn.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';\n      document.querySelectorAll('.start-here-faq-btn').forEach(function(b) {\n        b.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');\n        b.nextElementSibling.classList.remove('is-open');\n      });\n      if (!isOpen) {\n        btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');\n        btn.nextElementSibling.classList.add('is-open');\n      }\n    });\n  });\n</script>\n",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
    }
  },
